The paper proposes a method for a sentence-level answer-selection task in natural language processing, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also utilizes a latent clustering method, which could potentially fall under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
